javax.accessibility.Accessible, Directions, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, WorldBuilderInterface
public class MiniBuilder
extends java.awt.Frame
implements Directions, WorldBuilderInterface

A world builder suitable for use in Applets. Has all of the features of WorldBuilder except the file functionality. It will optionally make the world's speed control dialog visible.
